                        <h3><a href="<%= forum_path + '/general' %>">General talk</a></h3>
                        <p>Found a new tune? Think obis are the ugliest thing since plastic CD covers? Discuss it here!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="activity"><p>Last updated by <%= board_last_updated('general').user.username %> in thread "<%= board_last_updated('general').title %>" <br> at <%= board_last_updated('general').updated_at.strftime("%R %Z, %F") %></p></div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="<%= forum_path + '/newcomer' %>"><ion-icon name="ios-arrow-dropright-circle"></ion-icon></a>
                    <div class="board-title-container">
                        <h3><a href="<%= forum_path + '/newcomer' %>">Newcomer board</a></h3>
